channel.title: Looking for experienced Server Makers. Co-Owner spot reward!
channel.description: Hi, I just recently tried to make my own server, but I got too confused. Too complicated for myself. So... I decided to have somebody else do it, and in exchange i'll give them full Co-Owner privileges. I'll also guarantee them a lifetime spot on my server as Co-Admin, you can never be removed from ym server unless you want me to do so! So, if you think you can integrate my ideas for the server then I accept you. I have both an AIM and a YAHOO account. My name on both is DrunkM0nk3yz. Please help me out!
